data.description: Brand new, energy-efficient home available by Aug 2023! A unique single-story home featuring a social living area. White cabinets with hardware, cream/black granite countertops, travertine-look tile flooring and warm grey carpet in our Crisp package. Your family will love spending time outside at the community pool, playgrounds, walking trails and sports fields. Each energy-efficient home also comes standard with features that go beyond helping you save on utility bills--they allow your whole family to live better and breathe easier too.* Each of our homes is built with innovative, energy-efficient features designed to help you enjoy more savings, better health, real comfort and peace of mind.
